cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new adaptive learning rate algorithm for training deep neural networks. It may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks. Additionally, since the proposed algorithm is evaluated on image classification tasks, it may also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper's focus on deep learning and optimization techniques also suggests it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
